Cell.Text: It means he is the Master.
What shrine?
[S] Why, the shrine for Miraak.
Where can I find him?
You don't find Miraak. He finds you.
Why are you building a shrine?
Because we didn't have one.

He is the Master.
What shrine?
[S] The shrine outside of town. At the Earth Stone.
Where is he?

[S] The shrine for Miraak, of course.

[S] I mean simply that. The Master deserves the best shrine we can build.
